title: Pressure Transducer Swap, Level 5_1
description: At level 5_1, Wells 15 & 16 had their pressure transducers swapped out for newer upgraded models (CS450 to CS451).  Old transducers are working fine and are redeployed at Level 4_1. ^M Well 15 --> Well 7, Well 16 --> Well 5.    ^M ^M The new transducers are almost identical to the old ones and will output the same values. There should be little change. incident report migrated from SensorDB.
